      "id": "PopularPost57296",
      "post_content": "This card is epic. It never plays as less than a 6/6 in mono-black, and a 6/6 flier for ![6](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=6&type=symbol) is above-par. But it grows. When it attacks, it will probably be 7/7. Put [Shade's Form](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shade's Form) on it and the game ends very quickly. This was the first really good card I got, and it has a place in my heart along with shiny Thorn Elemental. This is the best-illustrated version of this around, by the way. 5/5",
