      "id": "PopularPost264597",
      "post_content": "@vantha  \n  \nNightmare is a horse because in the 1st ed. AD&D Monster Manual it's a horse. And Gygax got the idea, in part, from Fuseli's painting \"The Nightmare.\" In fact, D&D was a massive influence on the Alpha of Magic. it slays me how people don't know these things.",
